	(text "| Function      | MCU Pin         | Notes                                    |\n| ------------- | --------------- | ---------------------------------------- |\n| SWDIO         | PA13            | Debug/programming                        |\n| SWCLK         | PA14            | Debug/programming, shared with BOOT0 pin |\n| NRST          | PF2             | Hardware reset                           |\n| BQ UART TX    | PB6             | MCU → BQ79600                            |\n| BQ UART RX    | PB7             | BQ79600 → MCU                            |\n| Shunt I2C SCL | PB8             | I2C1_SCL                                 |\n| Shunt I2C SDA | PB9             | I2C1_SDA                                 |\n| CAN RX        | PD0             | FDCAN1_RX                                |\n| CAN TX        | PD1             | FDCAN1_TX                                |\n| CAN STBY      | PD2             | GPIO to CAN transceiver standby          |\n| Shunt ALERT   | PB5             | GPIO/EXTI input                          |\n| BQ FAULT_N    | PB4             | Active-low fault input from BQ79600      |\n| +3V3          | VDD/VDDA, VREF+ | Main MCU supply / reference              |\n| GND           | VSS/VSSA        | Ground                                   |\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 154.94 221.488 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "09c24734-d13e-4280-8460-36582af5d2d0")
	)
